<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>1LIFE — One-Decrypt Encryption</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#080808;--surface:#0f0f0f;--card:#111;--border:#1e1e1e;--border2:#2a2a2a;
  --red:#e63b2e;--red-dim:#7a1f18;--red-glow:#e63b2e40;
  --amber:#d97706;--green:#16a34a;--blue:#2563eb;--purple:#7c3aed;
  --text:#e8e6e0;--muted:#6b6560;
  --mono:'DM Mono',monospace;--serif:'Instrument Serif',serif;--display:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");opacity:.025;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999}
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:2rem}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 60%,#e63b2e0a 0%,transparent 70%),radial-gradient(ellipse 30% 30% at 20% 20%,#e63b2e05 0%,transparent 60%);pointer-events:none}
.hero-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(255,255,255,.008) 2px,rgba(255,255,255,.008) 4px);pointer-events:none}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.3em;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:1.5rem;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .8s .2s forwards}
.hero-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(7rem,20vw,18rem);line-height:.85;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:var(--text);text-align:center;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .8s .4s forwards}
.hero-title span{color:var(--red);display:inline-block;position:relative}
.hero-title span::before,.hero-title span::after{content:'1';position:absolute;inset:0;color:var(--red)}
.hero-title span::before{animation:glitch1 4s infinite;clip-path:polygon(0 20%,100% 20%,100% 40%,0 40%);transform:translateX(-2px);opacity:.7}
.hero-title span::after{animation:glitch2 4s infinite;clip-path:polygon(0 60%,100% 60%,100% 80%,0 80%);transform:translateX(2px);color:#d97706;opacity:.5}
.hero-sub{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(1rem,2.5vw,1.4rem);color:var(--muted);margin-top:1.5rem;text-align:center;max-width:500px;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .8s .6s forwards}
.hero-cta{display:flex;gap:1rem;margin-top:3rem;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp .8s .8s forwards;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.btn{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.75rem 2rem;border:1px solid;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block}
.btn-red{background:var(--red);border-color:var(--red);color:#fff}.btn-red:hover{background:transparent;color:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 30px var(--red-glow)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--muted)}.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--text);color:var(--text)}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:2rem;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 1s 1.2s forwards}
.scroll-line{width:1px;height:40px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--red),transparent);animation:scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.stats-bar{border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;overflow-x:auto}
.stat{flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:1.5rem 2rem;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}.stat:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-num{font-family:var(--display);font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--red);line-height:1}
.stat-label{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:.25rem}
.section{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 2rem}
.section-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:2rem}
.section-tag::before{content:'';display:block;width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--red)}
.section-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,6rem);line-height:.9;letter-spacing:.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.divider{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,var(--border2),transparent)}
.how-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);margin-top:3rem}
.how-card{background:var(--card);padding:2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.how-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--red);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .4s}
.how-card:hover::before{transform:scaleX(1)}
.how-num{font-family:var(--display);font-size:5rem;color:var(--border2);line-height:1;position:absolute;top:1rem;right:1.5rem;transition:color .3s}
.how-card:hover .how-num{color:var(--red-dim)}
.how-title{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:.75rem}
.how-body{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;position:relative;z-index:1}
.tool-area{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:5rem 0}
.tool-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem}
.tool-tabs{display:flex;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.tab-btn{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:1rem 2rem;background:transparent;border:none;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;position:relative;bottom:-1px}
.tab-btn.active{color:var(--text);border-bottom-color:var(--red)}
.tab-btn:hover:not(.active){color:var(--text)}
.tab-panel{display:none;padding-top:2rem}.tab-panel.active{display:block}
.mode-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(175px,1fr));gap:8px;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.mode-card{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border2);padding:1rem 1.25rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;position:relative}
.mode-card:hover{border-color:var(--muted)}.mode-card.selected{border-color:var(--red);background:#150808}
.mode-card.selected::after{content:'✓';position:absolute;top:.5rem;right:.75rem;color:var(--red);font-size:12px}
.mode-name{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:.3rem}
.mode-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
.mode-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.15rem .5rem;margin-top:.4rem;border:1px solid}
.badge-red{color:var(--red);border-color:var(--red-dim)}.badge-blue{color:#60a5fa;border-color:#1e3a5f}
.badge-green{color:#4ade80;border-color:#14532d}.badge-purple{color:#c084fc;border-color:#4c1d95}.badge-amber{color:#fbbf24;border-color:#78350f}
.tool-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2rem}
.field-group{margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.field-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.5rem;display:block}
textarea,input[type=text],input[type=password],input[type=file]{width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;padding:.875rem 1rem;resize:vertical;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;line-height:1.6}
textarea:focus,input:focus{border-color:var(--red)}
textarea{min-height:120px}
input[type=file]{cursor:pointer;padding:.75rem 1rem}
input[type=file]::-webkit-file-upload-button{background:var(--border2);border:none;color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;padding:.4rem 1rem;cursor:pointer;margin-right:1rem;letter-spacing:.1em}
.btn-action{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.875rem 2.5rem;background:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--red);color:#fff;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem}
.btn-action:hover{background:transparent;color:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 40px var(--red-glow)}
.btn-action:disabled{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed;pointer-events:none}
.btn-action-ghost{background:transparent;border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--muted)}.btn-action-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--text);color:var(--text);box-shadow:none}
.btn-row{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.output-box{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:1.25rem;min-height:70px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted);word-break:break-all;white-space:pre-wrap;position:relative;margin-top:1.5rem}
.output-box.has-content{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border2)}
.output-box.success{border-left:3px solid var(--green)}.output-box.error{border-left:3px solid var(--red);color:#ff6b6b}
.output-box.warning{border-left:3px solid var(--amber);color:#fbbf24}.output-box.destroyed{border-left:3px solid var(--red);background:#0d0404;color:#ff6060}
.copy-btn{position:absolute;top:.75rem;right:.75rem;background:var(--border2);border:none;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;padding:.3rem .75rem;cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .2s}.copy-btn:hover{color:var(--text);background:#333}
.status-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.dot-red{background:var(--red)}.dot-green{background:var(--green)}.dot-amber{background:var(--amber)}
.status-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:1rem;padding-top:1rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.blob-meta{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(155px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--border);margin-top:1rem}
.blob-meta-item{background:var(--bg);padding:.75rem 1rem}
.blob-meta-key{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase}
.blob-meta-val{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);margin-top:.2rem}
.progress-bar{height:2px;background:var(--border);overflow:hidden;margin-top:1rem;display:none}.progress-bar.active{display:block}
.progress-fill{height:100%;background:var(--red);width:0%;transition:width .3s}
.download-area{background:#0a150a;border:1px solid #16a34a33;border-left:3px solid var(--green);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:none;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-top:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.download-area.show{display:flex}.download-info{flex:1}.download-name{font-size:13px;color:var(--text)}.download-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:.2rem}
.btn-download{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.6rem 1.5rem;background:var(--green);border:none;color:#fff;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:opacity .2s}.btn-download:hover{opacity:.85}
.callout{background:#1a0a0a;border:1px solid var(--red-dim);border-left:3px solid var(--red);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.callout-icon{color:var(--red);font-size:1.1rem;flex-shrink:0}.callout-text{font-size:12px;color:#ff9999;line-height:1.6}
.callout.amber{background:#1a1400;border-color:#78350f;border-left-color:var(--amber)}.callout.amber .callout-icon,.callout.amber .callout-text{color:#fbbf24}
.destroyed-banner{background:#1a0000;border:1px solid var(--red);padding:1.5rem 2rem;text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;display:none}
.destroyed-banner.show{display:block}.destroyed-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.destroyed-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.algo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2rem;margin-top:3rem}
.algo-block{padding:2rem;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-top:2px solid var(--red)}
.algo-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:1rem}
.code-line{font-size:12px;line-height:2;color:var(--muted);padding:.1rem 0}
.code-line .kw{color:#c084fc}.code-line .fn{color:#60a5fa}.code-line .str{color:#34d399}.code-line .op{color:var(--red)}.code-line .cm{color:#374151;font-style:italic}
.spinner{width:14px;height:14px;border:2px solid transparent;border-top-color:currentColor;border-radius:50%;animation:spin .6s linear infinite;display:none;flex-shrink:0}.loading .spinner{display:block}
footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:3rem 2rem;text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em}
.footer-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--border2);margin-bottom:.5rem;letter-spacing:.05em}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes glitch1{0%,90%,100%{transform:translateX(0);opacity:0}92%{transform:translateX(-3px);opacity:.7}94%{transform:translateX(2px);opacity:.5}96%{transform:translateX(-1px);opacity:.3}}
@keyframes glitch2{0%,90%,100%{transform:translateX(0);opacity:0}93%{transform:translateX(3px);opacity:.5}95%{transform:translateX(-2px);opacity:.4}97%{transform:translateX(1px);opacity:.2}}
@keyframes scrollPulse{0%,100%{opacity:.3;transform:scaleY(1)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scaleY(1.1)}}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
@media(max-width:700px){.how-grid,.algo-grid,.mode-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.hero-title{font-size:7rem}.stats-bar{flex-wrap:wrap}.stat{min-width:50%;border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">One message. One chance.</p>
  <h1 class="hero-title"><span>1</span>LIFE</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Encryption that destroys itself after a single read.<br>No servers. No cloud. Pure mathematics.</p>
  <div class="hero-cta">
    <a href="#tool" class="btn btn-red">Encrypt Now</a>
    <a href="#how" class="btn btn-ghost">How It Works</a>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint"><div class="scroll-line"></div>Scroll</div>
</section>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">1×</div><div class="stat-label">ODE decryption</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">256</div><div class="stat-label">AES key bits</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">Cipher modes</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">3</div><div class="stat-label">Destroy layers</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">0</div><div class="stat-label">Servers needed</div></div>
</div>

<section id="how" class="section">
  <div class="section-tag">Protocol</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">HOW<br>IT WORKS</h2>
  <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:540px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;">ODE uses three independent layers to enforce one-decrypt. Even if you keep the original file, all three layers must pass — and after decryption, all three are permanently tripped.</p>
  <div class="how-grid">
    <div class="how-card"><div class="how-num">01</div><div class="how-title">Layer 1 — Fingerprint DB</div><div class="how-body">Before anything, a SHA-256 fingerprint of the blob is checked against localStorage. If found, decryption is blocked — even if you re-upload the original untouched file.</div></div>
    <div class="how-card"><div class="how-num">02</div><div class="how-title">Layer 2 — Header Zeros</div><div class="how-body">After successful decrypt, salt + nonce + hash chain are overwritten with zeros in the file. Re-opening the destroyed file fails the zero-check before any crypto runs.</div></div>
    <div class="how-card"><div class="how-num">03</div><div class="how-title">Layer 3 — Chain Verify</div><div class="how-body">SHA3-512 hash chain binds key + nonce + salt. Tampering any byte breaks the chain. Zeroed header also breaks the chain — double-enforcing destruction.</div></div>
    <div class="how-card"><div class="how-num">04</div><div class="how-title">Multi-Mode Support</div><div class="how-body">Beyond ODE, choose standard AES-256-GCM, ChaCha20-Poly1305, AES-CBC+HMAC, or Hybrid RSA+AES for use cases that allow multiple decrypts with a password.</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:3rem">
  <div class="section-tag">Algorithm</div>
  <div class="algo-grid">
    <div class="algo-block">
      <div class="algo-label">ODE Encrypt</div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="cm">// Ephemeral — never stored directly</span></div>
      <div class="code-line">salt,nonce <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">random</span>(<span class="str">32B, 16B</span>)</div>
      <div class="code-line">K <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">SHA3-256</span>(salt <span class="op">||</span> nonce)</div>
      <div class="code-line">H <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">SHA3-512</span>(K <span class="op">||</span> nonce <span class="op">||</span> salt)</div>
      <div class="code-line">C,tag <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">AES-256-GCM</span>(P, K, nonce)</div>
      <div class="code-line">blob <span class="op">=</span> magic<span class="op">+</span>salt<span class="op">+</span>nonce<span class="op">+</span>H<span class="op">+</span>tag<span class="op">+</span>C</div>
    </div>
    <div class="algo-block">
      <div class="algo-label">ODE Decrypt — 3 Layers</div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="cm">// Layer 1: fingerprint blacklist</span></div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="kw">if</span> <span class="fn">SHA256</span>(blob[:128]) <span class="kw">in</span> localStorage: <span class="fn">BLOCK</span></div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="cm">// Layer 2: zero-header check</span></div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="kw">if</span> salt<span class="op">==</span><span class="str">0x00</span> <span class="kw">or</span> nonce<span class="op">==</span><span class="str">0x00</span>: <span class="fn">BLOCK</span></div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="cm">// Layer 3: chain verify + decrypt</span></div>
      <div class="code-line">K <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">SHA3-256</span>(salt<span class="op">||</span>nonce); <span class="fn">verify</span> H</div>
      <div class="code-line">P <span class="op">=</span> <span class="fn">AES-GCM-Dec</span>(C,K,nonce)</div>
      <div class="code-line"><span class="cm">// Destroy + record</span></div>
      <div class="code-line">blob[4..116] <span class="op">=</span> <span class="str">zeros</span>; localStorage.<span class="fn">add</span>(fp)</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="tool" class="tool-area">
  <div class="tool-inner">
    <div class="section-tag">Interactive Tool</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:2rem">TRY IT<br>NOW</h2>
    <div class="tool-tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('encrypt',this)">⬛ Encrypt</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('decrypt',this)">🔓 Decrypt</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ENCRYPT TAB -->
    <div id="tab-encrypt" class="tab-panel active">
      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="callout">
          <div class="callout-icon">⚠</div>
          <div class="callout-text">ODE blobs can only be decrypted <strong>once</strong>. Three independent layers enforce this. After decryption, recovery is mathematically impossible. Download and store the file carefully.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
          <label class="field-label">Encryption Mode</label>
          <div class="mode-grid" id="enc-mode-grid">
            <div class="mode-card selected" data-mode="ode" onclick="selectMode(this)">
              <div class="mode-name">ODE · 1-Life</div>
              <div class="mode-desc">AES-256-GCM + SHA3-512 hash chain. 3-layer destroy. Self-destructs.</div>
              <span class="mode-badge badge-red">One-Decrypt</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mode-card" data-mode="aes-gcm" onclick="selectMode(this)">
              <div class="mode-name">AES-256-GCM</div>
              <div class="mode-desc">Password-based. Authenticated encryption. Industry standard.</div>
              <span class="mode-badge badge-blue">Multi-use</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mode-card" data-mode="chacha20" onclick="selectMode(this)">
              <div class="mode-name">ChaCha20-Poly1305</div>
              <div class="mode-desc">Password-based stream cipher. Fast on mobile hardware.</div>
              <span class="mode-badge badge-green">Fast</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mode-card" data-mode="aes-cbc" onclick="selectMode(this)">
              <div class="mode-name">AES-256-CBC</div>
              <div class="mode-desc">Password-based. Classic block cipher + HMAC-SHA256.</div>
              <span class="mode-badge badge-amber">Classic</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mode-card" data-mode="hybrid" onclick="selectMode(this)">
              <div class="mode-name">Hybrid RSA+AES</div>
              <div class="mode-desc">RSA-2048 wraps AES-256-GCM session key. Asymmetric.</div>
              <span class="mode-badge badge-purple">Asymmetric</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field-group">
